/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a moment on a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a driver's eye view of the scene. The sky above is a clear blue, providing a stark contrast to the urban landscape below. Buildings of various sizes and designs line the street, interspersed with trees that add a touch of green to the concrete jungle. Power lines crisscross above, forming a complex web against the sky. Cars of different makes and models are scattered along the road, hinting at the city's vibrant life. The image is taken from a low angle, which emphasizes the height of the buildings and the expanse of the sky. The colors in the image are vibrant, with the blue of the sky and the green of the trees standing out against the more muted tones of the buildings and cars.
